docs/working/digests/epic-002-platform-auth.md:64:  - 002EYA must finish the incomplete 002EY visual-regression contract by committing real Playwright screenshot baselines, making `npm run e2e` pass without `--update-snapshots`, failing fast when `E2E_DJANGO_PYTHON` is unset, and guarding `seed_e2e_users` so predictable E2E users cannot be seeded outside explicit local/E2E setup.
