docs/slices/002G-admin-user-and-role-management-shell.md:11:Give a `system_admin` a read + assignment shell over the existing seeded identity catalogue: list staff users, view one user's roles/teams/status, and change a user's role assignments, team memberships, and active status — all through the backend service/envelope path, never by inventing new business rules.
docs/slices/002G-admin-user-and-role-management-shell.md:17:- 002EYA
docs/slices/002G-admin-user-and-role-management-shell.md:18:- 002F
