docs/slices/002G-admin-user-and-role-management-shell.md:56:Implement only the admin user catalogue read/assignment endpoints named above. Reuse the existing identity models, session-bound auth helper, standard envelope helper, and audit-log model; do not add free-text role, permission, or team creation.
docs/slices/002G-admin-user-and-role-management-shell.md:59:Prefer no schema change. If a gap is found, keep it non-destructive and limited to existing identity/access needs; do not alter the seeded permission catalogue except through existing `Role`/`Permission` rows.
