docs/slices/002I-object-level-permission-test-harness.md:82:- Backend TDD: actor without the required canonical permission -> denied as missing permission.
docs/slices/002I-object-level-permission-test-harness.md:83:- Backend TDD: actor with permission but mismatched owner/team -> denied as object access denied.
