- [x] Tests written first (RED saved, then GREEN)
- [x] Code implemented
- [x] API contracts updated, if needed
- [x] Permissions tested
- [x] Tests/typecheck/lint/build passed
- [x] Risk assessment completed
- [x] Handoff updated
- [x] State updated
- [ ] Commit created only after passing gates

